  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fantastic spa facilities</strong></p>
<p>The 3,500m² spa at the Adler Spa Resort is a must visit during your stay, facilities here include: </p>
<ul>
<li>Heated outdoor pool with whirlpool with spectacular mountain views</li>
<li>Spa area with heated indoor pool, sauna area and relaxation area with loungers and water beds</li>
<li>Massages and treatments (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Free guided hikes Monday-Saturday and Nordic walking two or three times a week</li>
<li>Free e-bike hire</li>
<li>Free e-bike tours Monday - Saturday</li>
<li>Free daily programme of fitness and yoga classes</li>
<li>Piano bar five times a week and live music twice a week</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Fitness Room </li>
<li>Garden</li>
<li>Garage and parking (free)<span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></li>
<li>Kids Club for children aged 4-10 years old operating at set times all season</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
